title: Little Boy Beats His Mom in Waiting Room! | Qui West | 99.1 KGGI
text:
Little Boy Beats His Mom in Waiting Room! posted by Qui West - share 
I wish I had tried to raise my hand up on my mom when I was this kids age. I wouldn't be here today to even share this video with you. Qui West began his radio journey in 2006 as an intern in San Francisco where he developed a love for radio. From there, he became a public affairs host and landed a weekend on air spot with KYLD Wild 949. The he hit the majors and worked at Houston's legendary hip hop station KBXX 979 The Box. Qui West hosted the No.1 rated night show in the market for almost 4 years. Most recently, he was home in San Francisco at KRBQ 102. Now he has a new home, right here in the I.E. on 99.1 KGGI. Join him every afternoon from 2-6p and follow him everywhere @QuiWest. Contact
